{"tid":445619,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[電腦白痴Laptop換SSD急問","createTime":"2017-10-23T14:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T08:29:03.000Z","uid":79172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7cca15f6ae497d63d90968e518778531b41885","tid":445619,"uid":79172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"想問如果laptop hdd換ssd後想重新window的話，以下兩種情況係咪應該咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\nCase 1: 無Recovery Disk/Image = 換之前將hdd成個抄落去ssd，之後再裝，即開即用windows<br />\n<br />\nCase2: 有Recovery Disk/Image = 直接換左ssd落去，之後先用Recovery Disk/Image黎裝windows<br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7363eb3f930046d88fabfe6b246bcc7072733123","tid":445619,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"備份重要資料先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e0fdfdda2b0444bd7955dc6433469ffdc3ee1e","tid":445619,"uid":73695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"某些SSD會送CLONE SOFTWARE比你成個HDD COPY落SSD<br />\nCLONE完插上去就可以即用"},{"pid":"7ee3cc13d951404361c480b5864161a93f950272","tid":445619,"uid":79172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>某些SSD會送CLONE SOFTWARE比你成個HDD COPY落SSD<br />\nCLONE完插上去就可以即用</blockquote><br />\n我果個肯定無...同埋想問換左ssd後係咪直接入Recovery Disk/USB 再開機就可以直接入裝windows程序而唔駛去boot menu到較任何野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40955219f5dadd3747aa32e0e405240d4197b23d","tid":445619,"uid":79172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18871b7615dc4ea8d50fc7825b085d0bdf4ad437","tid":445