ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>clone最方便</blockquote><br />\n通常都係ga la"},{"pid":"7d1e08d79847846a00e75031ecbeb4ec36f33d8f","tid":445619,"uid":4754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔clone呢? clone左一了百了<br />\n冇未dl &hellip;有freeware clone的<br />\n<br />\n記住做乜之前都要backup好</blockquote><br />\n但有無得淨係clone個window os？其餘d野我100%肯定唔要</blockquote><br />\nClone 完再reset咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60f7523bb5436c689100b59067faf98954a200e","tid":445619,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T08:29:03.000Z","msg":"淨係要windowd唔要資料點解唔直接插usb重裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}